## 🏗️ Code Structure Patterns

### Backend Services (NestJS) - Standard Structure

Tất cả backend services tuân theo cấu trúc NestJS module-based pattern:

```
packages/2-services/{service-name}/
├── src/
│   ├── main.ts                      # Service entry point (gRPC server)
│   ├── app.module.ts                # Root module (imports all feature modules)
│   │
│   ├── 📁 modules/                  # Feature modules (domain-driven)
│   │   ├── 📁 {feature-name}/       # Each feature = one module
│   │   │   ├── {feature}.module.ts  # Module definition
│   │   │   ├── {feature}.service.ts # Business logic
│   │   │   ├── {feature}.controller.ts # gRPC controller (if needed)
│   │   │   ├── dto/                 # Data Transfer Objects
│   │   │   │   └── *.dto.ts         # DTOs for this feature
│   │   │   └── entities/            # Prisma entities (if feature-specific)
│   │   │
│   │   └── ...                      # Other feature modules
│   │
│   ├── 📁 controllers/              # gRPC Controllers (implements proto files)
│   │   └── {service}.controller.ts  # Main gRPC controller
│   │
│   ├── 📁 prisma/                   # Database layer
│   │   ├── schema.prisma            # Prisma schema (all entities)
│   │   └── migrations/              # Database migrations
│   │
│   ├── 📁 common/                    # Shared utilities
│   │   ├── decorators/              # Custom decorators
│   │   ├── filters/                 # Exception filters
│   │   ├── guards/                  # Auth guards
│   │   ├── interceptors/            # Interceptors
│   │   └── pipes/                   # Validation pipes
│   │
│   └── 📁 config/                    # Configuration
│       ├── database.config.ts       # Database config
│       └── grpc.config.ts          # gRPC config
│
├── proto/                            # Protocol Buffer definitions
│   └── {service}.proto              # gRPC service definition
│
├── package.json
├── tsconfig.json
└── README.md
```

**Key Patterns:**
- **Module-based**: Mỗi feature = một module độc lập
- **Service Layer**: Business logic trong `*.service.ts`
- **DTO Pattern**: Tất cả DTOs import từ `7-shared`, không hard-code
- **Prisma**: Database access qua Prisma ORM
- **gRPC Controllers**: Implement proto files từ `7-shared`

### Gateway Service (NestJS) - BFF Pattern

```
packages/1-gateway/
├── src/
│   ├── main.ts                      # Express/Fastify server entry
│   ├── app.module.ts                # Root module
│   │
│   ├── 📁 modules/
│   │   ├── 📁 auth/                 # Authentication module
│   │   │   ├── auth.module.ts
│   │   │   ├── auth.guard.ts        # JWT validation guard
│   │   │   └── auth.service.ts      # Auth logic
│   │   │
│   │   ├── 📁 {resource}/           # Resource modules (users, stories, etc.)
│   │   │   ├── {resource}.module.ts
│   │   │   ├── {resource}.controller.ts  # REST/GraphQL controller
│   │   │   ├── {resource}.service.ts     # Aggregates data from services
│   │   │   └── dto/                 # Request/Response DTOs
│   │   │
│   │   └── 📁 graphql/              # GraphQL module
│   │       ├── graphql.module.ts
│   │       ├── resolvers/           # GraphQL resolvers
│   │       └── schemas/            # GraphQL schemas
│   │
│   ├── 📁 grpc/                     # gRPC clients
│   │   ├── clients/                # gRPC client stubs
│   │   └── interfaces/             # Service interfaces
│   │
│   └── 📁 common/                   # Shared utilities
│       ├── filters/                # Exception filters
│       ├── interceptors/           # Response interceptors
│       └── decorators/             # Custom decorators
│
└── package.json
```

**Key Patterns:**
- **BFF (Backend for Frontend)**: Aggregates data from multiple services
- **No Business Logic**: Gateway chỉ routing, auth, rate limiting
- **gRPC Clients**: Calls backend services via gRPC
- **REST + GraphQL**: Exposes both REST API and GraphQL

